WARNING: Pre-alpha code, PROCEED AT YOUR OWN RISK!

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
-------------------
- PHP 5 with cURL extension enabled
- Smarty (http://smarty.net)
- MySQL 5


INSTALLATION
------------
SET UP DATABASE:
- Create a database and select it, i.e., 
CREATE DATABASE twitalytic
- Build tables with build_db.sql
CONFIGURE CODE:
- Edit twitalytic/include/config.inc.php, add your Twitter user id, name, password (blech!), db credentials and paths
- Edit twitalytic/automated/crawl.config.inc.php, set crawler include path to twitalytic/include

CONFIGURE WEBSERVER:
- Set httpd.conf DocumentRoot to twitalytic/www/


RUN CRAWLER TO LOAD DATA
------------------------
Watch what's going on:
$ tail -f automated/logs/crawl.log

Run crawler:
$ php automated/crawl.php

Cron this job to run once per hour

Once there's data in the DB, view webapp in http://localhost/